[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    131[0m:[38;5;10m[49m   The pseudocode does not show or describe the dedup logic.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    132[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - **Fix:** Either (a) add the dedup-and-reconciliation logic explicitly to the pseudocode in Step 5, or (b) add a short prose paragraph just before the pseudocode explaining that real production implementations of `apply_treatment_change` must reconcile pre-existing treatment with the requested change rather than blindly appending. Option (a) is the clearer teaching choice. Suggested pseudocode addition:
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    133[0m:[38;5;10m[49m   ```
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    134[0m:[38;5;10m[49m   FUNCTION apply_treatment_change(base_timeline, change, anchor_time):
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    135[0m:[38;5;10m[49m       modified = copy(base_timeline)
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    136[0m:[38;5;10m[49m       IF change.action == "add":
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    137[0m:[38;5;10m[49m           drug_class = change.drug_class
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    138[0m:[38;5;10m[49m           // Reconcile against pre-existing exposure. A patient already on
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    139[0m:[38;5;10m[49m           // the requested class does not get a second modifier applied; the
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    140[0m:[38;5;10m[49m           // counterfactual is a no-op for them and should be flagged so the
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    141[0m:[38;5;10m[49m           // clinical surface can communicate "patient is already on this."
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    142[0m:[38;5;10m[49m           already_active = any(
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    143[0m:[38;5;10m[49m               tx.drug_class == drug_class
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    144[0m:[38;5;10m[49m               AND tx.start_months_from_zero <= anchor_time
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    145[0m:[38;5;10m[49m               AND (tx.end_months_from_zero is null
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    146[0m:[38;5;10m[49m                    OR tx.end_months_from_zero >= anchor_time)
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    147[0m:[38;5;10m[49m               FOR tx IN modified
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    148[0m:[38;5;10m[49m           )
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    149[0m:[38;5;10m[49m           IF NOT already_active:
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    150[0m:[38;5;10m[49m               modified.append({
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    151[0m:[38;5;10m[49m                   drug_class:             drug_class,
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    152[0m:[38;5;10m[49m                   start_months_from_zero: anchor_time + change.start_offset_months,
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    153[0m:[38;5;10m[49m                   end_months_from_zero:   null
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    154[0m:[38;5;10m[49m               })
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    155[0m:[38;5;10m[49m       // (similar reconciliation for swap and stop actions)
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    156[0m:[38;5;10m[49m       RETURN modified
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    157[0m:[38;5;10m[49m   ```
